Soap star Gillian Taylforth has been charged with drink driving after she was arrested early on Saturday.

Her fiancée Dave Fairbairn was also arrested for a public order offence as she was breathalysed. 

The pair were stopped at 1.25am on Saturday morning, five miles from her £900,000 Broxbourne home. 

