A Hertfordshire police spokesman told MailOnline: 'The 59-year-old was arrested at 1.25am on February 7 in Fore Street, Hertford. 

'She has been charged with drink driving and bailed to return to the North & East Hertfordshire Magistrates Court on February 23.'

He added: 'A 59-year-old man from Cambridgeshire who was a passenger was also arrested on suspicion of a public order offence and has been issued with a fixed penalty notice and released.' 

